OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772647566
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged serious assault
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched following the death of a 58-
OL,8,Fyear-old man after an alleged serious
OL,9,Fassault in Pencoed.
OL,11,FSouth Wales Police confirmed that the
OL,12,Fvictim, who had been in a critical
OL,13,Fcondition in hospital since the
OL,14,Fincident in the early hours of
OL,15,FSaturday, February 28th, passed away
OL,16,Fon Monday, March 2nd.
OL,18,FA 26-year-old man has been arrested in
OL,19,Fconnection with the incident, and
OL,20,Fremains in police custody.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
