OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772647566
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged serious assault
OL,6,FDetectives have stated they are not
OL,7,Fcurrently looking for anyone else, and
OL,8,Fthe investigation, is now being led by
OL,9,Fthe force's Major Crime Investigation
OL,10,FTeam.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Graham Williams,
OL,13,Ffrom the Major Crime Investigation
OL,14,FTeam, said the victim's family is
OL,15,Fbeing supported by specially trained
OL,16,Fofficers.
OL,18,F"Sadly, a 58-year-old man has died in
OL,19,Fhospital following the incident on
OL,20,FSaturday morning.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772647566
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged serious assault
OL,6,F"I would like to reassure the local
OL,7,Fcommunity that we have somebody in
OL,8,Fcustody and are not looking for
OL,9,Fanybody else at this time.
OL,11,F"I thank everyone in the community who
OL,12,Fhas helped our investigation so far,
OL,13,Fand I urge anyone with information
OL,14,Fwhich may be relevant, particularly
OL,15,Fthe two potential witnesses, to get in
OL,16,Ftouch."
OL,18,FOfficers are appealing for anyone who
OL,19,Fwas in the vicinity of Felindre Road
OL,20,Fbetween midnight and 5:00 AM on
OL,21,FSaturday to come forward.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
