OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772647566
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged serious assault
OL,6,FDetectives would like to speak to two
OL,7,Fpotential witnesses, two elderly
OL,8,Fpeople who are believed to have walked
OL,9,Falong Felindre Road between 12.30am
OL,10,Fand 4am on Saturday.
OL,12,FMotorists are urged to their check
OL,13,Fdashcams for any footage which may be
OL,14,Frelevant. The force asked anybody with
OL,15,Finformation to contact 101 quoting
OL,16,Freference 2600063517.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/4
